Package net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.components

Class TreeHandlerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.forms.ComponentHandlerImpl
      • net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.components.TreeHandlerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeHandler, ComponentHandler<Object>
    public class TreeHandlerImpl
extends ComponentHandlerImpl
implements TreeHandler
    A test implementation of the TreeHandler interface. This class provides some basic implementations for some of the methods defined by the TreeHandler interface. It can be used for tests with tags that do something with trees or their handlers.
    Version:
    $Id: TreeHandlerImpl.java 205 2012-01-29 18:29:57Z oheger $
    Author:
    Oliver Heger
